oji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5690789703146552a2e6d5221602d9ec698d625","tid":2126794,"uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T05:01:59.000Z","msg":"又死藍屍廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4576eeb00564b0fd0b94ebdd872cfffc68827662","tid":2126794,"uid":37814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T05:11:22.000Z","msg":"伊利沙伯醫院發言人今日（七月二十七日）公布，一名確診2019冠狀病毒病的92歲男病人（個案編號：1306）於早上離世。<br />\n <br />\n病人有長期病患，他於七月七日因氣促、咳嗽入住伊利沙伯醫院接受治療，病人情況持續惡化，醫院就病人的病情與家屬溝通，家屬同意若病人情況再轉差時，不為病人施行心肺復甦術，病人延至今日上午九時十三分離世。<br />\n <br />\n院方對病人離世感到難過，會為家屬提供適切協助。<br />\n <br />\n連同上述個案，至今共有20名2019冠狀病毒病確診病人於公立醫院離世。"},{"pid":"6c22470105a8ed51056763bfc2d4a9218402b56a","tid":2126794,"uid":159796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T05:12:18.000Z","msg":"RIP 比政府害死"},{"pid":"21c9569310de8cec2850a85bb0296620fdc07133","tid":2126794,"uid":69650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T05:13:02.000Z","msg":"d兒兒孫孫有冇出聲屌正苦"},{"pid":"b99bfaf26b0eeeda33326f8d0b98b416ede7b594","tid":2126794,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T05:14:25.000Z","msg":"本身都92,仲要長期病患者,都唔知關唔關廢炎事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783f387fd11014645f95591a89c81d6004ebac3d","tid":2126794,"uid":51127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T05:17:40.000Z","msg":"呢隻病直情係做緊每個國家都最想做既野，專殺老弱傷殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw, rip"}]}